      "text": [
        "396 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «لاَ تَدَعَنَّ مَيِّتَكَ وَحْدَهُ فَإِنَّ اَلشَّيْطَانَ يَعْبَثُ بِهِ فِي جَوْفِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.396 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Do not leave your deceased alone, for Shaytan may disturb them within their body.\""
